textBeforeTable: La Liga Carlos Pena has made more crosses without finding a teammate with one than any other player in La Liga this season (11). Alcatraz has committed four fouls in only 57 minutes of league football this season.. Of all the players to have taken over 10 penalties in La Liga since 2003/04, Diego Castro is the only one with a 100% success rate (15 out of 15). Oscar participated in all three goals that Valladolid scored against Getafe over both La Liga meetings last season (two goals, one assist). Getafe have not won an away game since the last time one of their players netted a brace in a league outing (Colunga in a 3-1 victory in Mallorca in February). Valladolid have lost five successive league games; they have not lost six in a row since 1997/98. The Blues have not won any of their four top-flight trips to Pucela (D2 L2). Valladolid have only three of their eight previous top-flight meetings with Getafe (D2 L3), though two came at the Zorrilla.
